General.Name: Tiv Taam
General.Description: Tiv Taam Holdings 1 Ltd., together with its subsidiaries produces, markets, and imports of food products in Israel. The company provides fruits and vegetables, meat and chicken products, fish and sea food, eggs, milk, salads, cheese products, sausages, breads and pastries, canned food pasta dressing and spreads, nuts, seeds, snacks, dried fruits, spices, frozen vegetables and fruits, frozen food and concentrates, and cereal snacks and sweets, such as oats, energy bars, halva, chocolates and candies, snacks, and cakes and cookies, as well as ice creams and ices. It also offers beverages, such as soda drinks, juices and nectars, syrups and concentrates, water, iced tea, hot beverages, and tea and infusions, as well as wine, beer, alcohol, cigarette products, and organic food and drinks. In addition, the company provides bath and cosmetics, housewares, kitchen products, toys, stationery and office products, electrical and lighting accessories, and home care and animal products. Further, it operates a chain of food retail stores, as well as sells its products through online. The company was formerly known as World Group Holdings Ltd. and changed its name to Tiv Taam Holdings 1 Ltd. in May 2007. Tiv Taam Holdings 1 Ltd. was incorporated in 1965 and is based in Hefer Valley, Israel.
